OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1774786269
OL,3,CMan accused of causing wife's suicide
OL,4,Csays her death was 'worst day of my
OL,5,Clife'
OL,7,FA man accused of causing his wife to
OL,8,Ftake her own life by controlling and
OL,9,Fabusing her has told a jury that
OL,10,Ffinding out about her death was "the
OL,11,Fworst day of my life".
OL,13,FChristopher Trybus, from Swindon, is
OL,14,Faccused of the manslaughter of Tarryn
OL,15,FBaird, who died by suicide in November
OL,16,F2017 at the age of 34.
OL,18,FHe also faces charges at Winchester
OL,19,FCrown Court of controlling and
OL,20,Fcoercive behaviour and two charges of
OL,21,Frape.
OL,26,@rD@aOUsD@UO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,437,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1774786269
OL,3,CMan accused of causing wife's suicide
OL,4,Csays her death was 'worst day of my
OL,5,Clife'
OL,7,FThe coercive control charge alleges
OL,8,Fthat Trybus controlled Ms Baird
OL,9,Fthrough using and threatening violence
OL,10,Ftowards her, sexually assaulting her,
OL,11,Fmonitoring her whereabouts, limiting
OL,12,Faccess to finance, threatening to
OL,13,Freveal private information to her
OL,14,Ffamily and isolating her from her
OL,15,Ffamily.
OL,17,FTrybus told the court that he was in
OL,18,FGermany when he received a call
OL,19,Finforming him of his wife's death.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,437,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1774786269
OL,3,CMan accused of causing wife's suicide
OL,4,Csays her death was 'worst day of my
OL,5,Clife'
OL,7,FThe 44-year-old said that as he was
OL,8,Fdriving to the airport to return home,
OL,9,Fhe "broke down" in tears.
OL,11,FHe said: "Halfway down the drive, I
OL,12,Fbroke down and cried. I got to the
OL,13,Fairport, dumped the car, asked them to
OL,14,Fput me at the front of the plane
OL,15,Fbecause I wanted to get out as soon as
OL,16,Fpossible.
OL,18,F"It's not something anyone can prepare
OL,19,Fthemselves for, it's a cliche but you
OL,20,Fnever think it's going to happen to
OL,21,Fyou.
OL,26,@qD@DOUqD@OO]sD@JOUzD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,437,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1774786269
OL,3,CMan accused of causing wife's suicide
OL,4,Csays her death was 'worst day of my
OL,5,Clife'
OL,7,F"So, worst day of my life, just
OL,8,Fabsolutely terrible, I don't know how
OL,9,Felse to describe it."
OL,11,FThe court has heard that Ms Baird had
OL,12,Fa history of mental health issues,
OL,13,Fincluding a diagnosis of potential
OL,14,FPTSD having witnessed "traumatic" car-
OL,15,Fjacking incidents in South Africa
OL,16,Fwhere the couple grew up before moving
OL,17,Fto the UK in 2007.
OL,26,@oD@AOUqD@UO]vD@WOUvD@aO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,437,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1774786269
OL,3,CMan accused of causing wife's suicide
OL,4,Csays her death was 'worst day of my
OL,5,Clife'
OL,7,FTrybus told the court that he believed
OL,8,FMs Baird's mental health had improved
OL,9,Fin the weeks before her death after
OL,10,Fshe had taken up a volunteer role for
OL,11,Fcourt witness support.
OL,13,FHe said that he thought she was
OL,14,F"mostly back to her normal self, she
OL,15,Fseemed to bounce back and be on the
OL,16,Fmend. I felt like things were starting
OL,17,Fto improve".
OL,26,@vD@AOUyD@KO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,437,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1774786269
OL,3,CMan accused of causing wife's suicide
OL,4,Csays her death was 'worst day of my
OL,5,Clife'
OL,7,FWhen asked how he felt about being
OL,8,Fabroad for work regularly in the
OL,9,Fmonths before her death, Trybus said:
OL,10,F"I wish I could have done more,
OL,11,Fpossibly I could have stayed home, I
OL,12,Fcould have taken some time off of work
OL,13,Fbut when you are in it, you do not see
OL,14,Fit, you just think it will never
OL,15,Fhappen."
OL,17,FWhen his barrister Katy Thorne KC
OL,18,Fasked him if he was a "violent and
OL,19,Fdomineering man", he replied: "No, I
OL,20,Fdo not think so".
OL,26,@rD@AOUwD@HO]zD@WOU{D@PO]{D@_OU|D@PO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,437,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1774786269
OL,3,CMan accused of causing wife's suicide
OL,4,Csays her death was 'worst day of my
OL,5,Clife'
OL,7,FWhen asked if he was responsible for
OL,8,FMs Baird's death, he replied: "No, not
OL,9,Fat all."
OL,11,FHe also denied raping, sexually
OL,12,Fassaulting, being violent towards her
OL,13,Fand controlling her.
OL,15,FWhen asked by prosecutor Tom Little KC
OL,16,Fif he was angry at being labelled a
OL,17,F"wife-beater" by his late wife who
OL,18,Faccused him of assaulting or sexually
OL,19,Fassaulting her on 25 occasions, Trybus
OL,20,Freplied: "It's difficult to be angry
OL,21,Fwith someone who is dead."
OL,26,@pD@_OUqD@HO]yD@AOUyD@MO]|D@JOU}D@ZO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,437,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1774786269
OL,3,CMan accused of causing wife's suicide
OL,4,Csays her death was 'worst day of my
OL,5,Clife'
OL,7,FHe added: "It's difficult to know what
OL,8,Fwas going on in her troubled mind.
OL,9,FIt's someone I love very dearly, I try
OL,10,Fto understand it, not get angry about
OL,11,Fit.
OL,13,F"Me being angry with her isn't going
OL,14,Fto change it, I try to hold on to good
OL,15,Fmemories we have."
OL,17,FThe defendant said he would have got
OL,18,F"upset, not necessarily angry" with Ms
OL,19,FBaird during arguments but had not
OL,20,Fshouted at her or lost his temper.
OL,26,@oD@KOUuD@AOUwD@RO]zD@AOUzD@^O]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
