OL,3,CMan accused of causing wife's suicide
OL,4,Csays her death was 'worst day of my
OL,5,Clife'
OL,7,FTrybus, who is a software consultant
OL,8,Fand developer, denies the charges and
OL,9,Fthe trial continues.
